  "intent": "Execute a cherry-picking protocol using a P300 multi-channel pipette to transfer effector cells from a 96-well deep plate to specific wells in a 384-well plate. The protocol parses CSV input to determine transfer volumes, source wells, and destination coordinates. For each column group, aspirate the specified effector cell volume from designated source wells in the deep plate, with optional pre-mixing at different heights, then dispense to corresponding wells in two rows of the 384-well plate (primary row and +24 offset row). Use dynamic tip pickup based on the highest row letter required per column, with configurable aspiration/dispense heights, flow rates, and mixing parameters.",
